        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the tomatoes are fragrant, add the<strong> tomato stock</strong> and<strong> crab meat</strong> to the pan and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Season with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until thickened to a pasta sauce-like consistency – this is your <strong>fiery tomato sauce</strong></p>",
